org.codehaus.jackson.map.deser

Class SettableBeanProperty.InnerClassProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codehaus.jackson.map.deser.SettableBeanProperty
      • org.codehaus.jackson.map.deser.SettableBeanProperty.InnerClassProperty
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BeanProperty, Named
    Enclosing class:
    SettableBeanProperty

    public static final class SettableBeanProperty.InnerClassProperty
extends SettableBeanProperty
    This sub-class is used to handle special case of value being a non-static inner class. If so, we will have to use a special alternative for default constructor; but otherwise can delegate to regular implementation.
    Since:
    1.9
